{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"49419-hum-chadhi-sakait-chhi","title":"I Can Climb! / हम चढ़ि सकैत छी","description":"Here, a little boy learns to climb up. But can he climb down? This book is one of the four books in the 'Growing Up' series.    एकटा छोट बच्चा  ऊपर चढ़नाइ तs सीख जाइत अछि । मुदा ओ नीचा उतरि पाओत की?\r\n","language":"Maithili","langCode":"mai","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kumar Vikramaditya"],"illustrators":["Deval Maniar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Aripana Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/49419-hum-chadhi-sakait-chhi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705479/size3/57c8c82ddc4444a38929edee69280586.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/705479/size6/57c8c82ddc4444a38929edee69280586.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10296/size6/181ab632f1a87a35d9047592ee73c38c.jpg","text":"I am a big boy now. \nआब हम एकटा सियान लड़का छी।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10297/size6/4d49fae924a80cb1af9ba6f2e58033ee.jpg","text":"I can climb up the steps. \nहम सिरही पर चढ़ि सकैत छी।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10299/size6/37cc47b386e17285c685aa226d0d09f8.jpg","text":"But I cannot climb down again. \nमुदा फेर हम नीचा नहि उतरि सकैत छी।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10300/size6/a6ed8b4d0dafcb56529321ac8f111794.jpg","text":"I can climb on a chair. \nहम कुर्सी पर चढ़ि सकैत छी।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10301/size6/817c63927008771778a8aa78fcf1d224.jpg","text":"But I cannot climb down again. \nमुदा फेर हम नीचा नहि उतरि सकैत छी।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10302/size6/e33f59a901dd498e821d63b844ec7a89.jpg","text":"I climb on to the chair, and then on the table! \nपहिने हम कुर्सी पर चढ़ब, तखन टेबुल पर!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10303/size6/aacafea6d668bb6e461660bd165c889b.jpg","text":"But I cannot climb down again. \nमुदा फेर हम नीचा नहि उतरि सकैत छी।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10304/size6/2f2ce99b6c18ca6bca6369c6d3cfda4b.jpg","text":"“Papa! Papa!” I shout. \n\"पापा! पापा!\" हम  चिकरलहूँ।\nPapa laughs. “Sonu, learn to climb down!” he says. \nपापा हँसैतकहलखिन, “सोनू! नीचा उतरब सीखू।“","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10305/size6/20a9267e0350248a07adf620252839a4.jpg","text":"I am afraid. But I do not cry. \nहम डेरा गेलौँ। मुदा हम कनलहुँ नहि।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10306/size6/8466d6307263a314c983d7a078f4ead3.jpg","text":"Slowly, I get down from the table, and down from the chair.\nनहुए सँ, हम टेबुल सँ नीचाँ उतरलहूँ,    कुर्सी \nसँ नीचाँ अएलहूँ ।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/10307/size6/65f45b5bdfd29af3ff6dcd55c33240b0.jpg","text":"At last, I have learnt to climb down too! \nअंत मे, हम निच्चहूँ उतरब सीखि गेलहूँ!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":175}}